      "text": "write %!data% to echo",
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Body writes back to its own channel name. The IsExecuting guard makes the\nregistry treat \u0022echo\u0022 as not-found while this body is running, so this\ninner write surfaces ChannelNotFound rather than recursing.",
